{"type":"text","timestamp":1775878395699,"sessionID":"ses_2856694b8ffeS5zMcuQ0zqL5Ss","part":{"id":"prt_d7a99b46b001P6JIt3qUAShuPj","messageID":"msg_d7a99aa7b001d56L5m2e22oGdH","sessionID":"ses_2856694b8ffeS5zMcuQ0zqL5Ss","type":"text","text":"## AR-029 — SDK HTTP 底层客户端 Archive\n\n### Completed\n\n**Phase 1-8: All tasks complete (ST-3 stage)**\n\n1. **Package Structure & Utilities** ✓\n   - `agentcube/__init__.py` with exports\n   - Exception hierarchy (`AgentCubeError`, `CommandExecutionError`, `SessionError`, `DataPlaneError`)\n   - HTTP session factory with connection pooling (10/10)\n   - Token reader, logger utilities\n\n2. **Control Plane Client** ✓\n   - `ControlPlaneClient` with Workload Manager integration\n   - Session creation/deletion endpoints\n   - Environment variable resolution (`WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL`)\n   - 404 idempotent handling on delete\n\n3. **Data Plane Clients** ✓\n   - `CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient`: execute commands, run code, file operations (upload/download/write/list)\n   - `AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient`: bootstrap session ID, invoke endpoint\n   - Router URL path building with `urljoin()`\n   - Session header management (`x-agentcube-session-id`)\n\n4. **Configuration & Environment** ✓\n   - Env var fallbacks (`ROUTER_URL`, `WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL`)\n   - Timeout defaults (120s read / 5.0s connect)\n   - Per-call timeout override\n   - Connection pool configuration\n\n5. **Error Handling** ✓\n   - ValueError for missing URLs/session headers\n   - `CommandExecutionError` with exit_code, stderr, command\n   - HTTP error propagation\n\n6. **High-Level Client Integration** ✓\n   - `CodeInterpreterClient` with context manager protocol\n   - `AgentRuntimeClient` with session bootstrapping\n   - Delegation methods to data plane clients\n\n7. **Session ID Management** ✓\n   - Bootstrap from Router invocation endpoint\n   - Explicit session ID support for reuse\n\n8. **URL Path Building** ✓\n   - All paths use `urljoin()` for relative path resolution\n\n---\n\n### Deferred\n\n**None** — All 18 acceptance criteria met. \n\nNotes from tasks.md:\n- `SessionError` and `DataPlaneError` defined but not raised (reserved for future expansion)\n- Async support explicitly deferred to future phase (see proposal alternatives)","time":{"start":1775878395697,"end":1775878395697}}}
